text: Forbes 30 Under 30 is a set of lists of 30 notable people under 30 years old. The people work in multiple professions. The list is issued every year by Forbes magazine. The final 30 under 30 list published by Forbes is divided into different categories of industries: Sport, Media, Social Enterprise, Hollywood & Entertainment, Science, Art & Style, Finance, Venture Capital, Games, Marketing & Advertising, Technology (Consumer and Enterprise), Education, Healthcare, Retail, Music, Food & Drink, Social Media, and Energy. ==References== Category:Lists of people 30 Under 30
title: Forbes 30 Under 30
